data.description: Come and experience Intown living in this adorable bungalow in the fastest growing community in Southwest Atlanta, Ashview Heights! Leave the car in the driveway and cycle to the beltline or to the new 11 acre multi-purpose green space for community events, and tailgating at the Mercedes Benz Stadium. This remodeled home boast 3 large bedrooms and a bonus room, which can be used as an office. Live in this thriving community with a committed neighborhood association before prices escalate!
data.whatILove: Off Street parking and a awesome backyard deck perfect for entertaining!
